"title": "8128: guidance, receiving God's",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8128: guidance, receiving god's",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>God's guidance is promised to those who genuinely desire it and seek it.</p>\n<h2>God's readiness to guide his people</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps25:4-Ps25:5\">PSA 25:4–25:5</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:5\">JAS 1:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod33:12-Exod33:16\">EXO 33:12–33:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job6:24\">JOB 6:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps5:8\">PSA 5:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps27:11\">PSA 27:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps31:3\">PSA 31:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps61:1-Ps61:2\">PSA 61:1–61:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps86:11\">PSA 86:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps143:8\">PSA 143:8</a></p>\n<h2>Guidance is given through the truth and counsel of God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps43:3\">PSA 43:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps16:7-Ps16:8\">PSA 16:7–16:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps73:23-Ps73:24\">PSA 73:23–73:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:35\">PSA 119:35</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:105\">PSA 119:105</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:133\">PSA 119:133</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:3-John10:4\">JHN 10:3–10:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:27\">JHN 10:27</a></p>\n<h2>Guidance is given to the humble and penitent</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov3:5-Prov3:6\">PRO 3:5–3:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr6:26-2Chr6:27\">2CH 6:26–6:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps25:9\">PSA 25:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps139:23-Ps139:24\">PSA 139:23–139:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa57:15\">ISA 57:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa57:18-Isa57:19\">ISA 57:18–57:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer50:4-Jer50:5\">JER 50:4–50:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek20:1-Ezek20:3\">EZK 20:1–20:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek20:30-Ezek20:31\">EZK 20:30–20:31</a></p>\n<h2>Guidance is given to those willing to obey God's will</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:39\">MAT 26:39</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:35-Mark14:36\">MRK 14:35–14:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:42\">LUK 22:42</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num14:8-Num14:9\">NUM 14:8–14:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps32:8-Ps32:9\">PSA 32:8–32:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa48:17-Isa48:18\">ISA 48:17–48:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:1-Rom12:2\">ROM 12:1–12:2</a></p>\n<h2>The role of the Holy Spirit in guidance</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:11-Luke12:12\">LUK 12:11–12:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps143:10\">PSA 143:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:13\">JHN 16:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:19-Acts10:20\">ACT 10:19–10:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:2\">ACT 13:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:6-Acts16:7\">ACT 16:6–16:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:18\">GAL 5:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:26-1John2:27\">1JN 2:26–2:27</a></p>\n<h2>Receiving guidance from Scripture</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:105\">PSA 119:105</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:133\">PSA 119:133</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps19:8\">PSA 19:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa8:19-Isa8:20\">ISA 8:19–8:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:11\">ACT 17:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:19\">2PE 1:19</a></p>\n<h2>Means of being guided by God</h2>\n<h3>The pillar of cloud and the pillar of fire</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod13:21-Exod13:22\">EXO 13:21–13:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod14:19-Exod14:20\">EXO 14:19–14:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:19\">NEH 9:19</a></p>\n<h3>The Urim and the Thummin</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:29-Exod28:30\">EXO 28:29–28:30</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num27:21\">NUM 27:21</a></p>\n<h3>The casting of lots</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam14:36-1Sam14:42\">1SA 14:36–14:42</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov16:33\">PRO 16:33</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah1:7\">JON 1:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:26\">ACT 1:26</a></p>\n<h3>Dreams and visions</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt2:19-Matt2:20\">MAT 2:19–2:20</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:10-Acts9:11\">ACT 9:10–9:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen40:5-Gen40:8\">GEN 40:5–40:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel2:28\">JOL 2:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:3-Acts10:6\">ACT 10:3–10:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts11:5-Acts11:9\">ACT 11:5–11:9</a></p>\n<h3>Angels</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:26\">ACT 8:26</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:19\">ACT 5:19</a></p>",
